"value) tuples, but could sometimes be instantiated as a tuple of tuples.  It "
"is now always a list."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGELOG.rst:378
msgid ""
"`#4039 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest/issues/4039>`_: No longer issue "
"warnings about using ``pytest_plugins`` in non-top-level directories when "
