"through porting the formerly external pytest-cache plugin into pytest core. "
"BACKWARD INCOMPAT: if you used pytest-cache's functionality to persist data "
"between test runs be aware that we don't serialize sets anymore. Thanks "
"Ronny Pfannschmidt for most of the merging work."
