"fixtures. Thanks Jason R. Coombs for reporting and Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3464
msgid ""
"added ``tmpdir_factory``, a session-scoped fixture that can be used to "
"create directories under the base temporary directory. Previously this "
"object was installed as a ``_tmpdirhandler`` attribute of the ``config`` "
"object, but now it is part of the official API and using ``config."
"_tmpdirhandler`` is deprecated. Thanks Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3471
msgid ""
"fix issue808: pytest's internal assertion rewrite hook now implements the "
"optional PEP302 get_data API so tests can access data files next to them. "
"Thanks xmo-odoo for request and example and Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3476
msgid ""
"rootdir and inifile are now displayed during usage errors to help users "
"diagnose problems such as unexpected ini files which add unknown options "
"being picked up by pytest. Thanks to Pavel Savchenko for bringing the "
"problem to attention in #821 and Bruno Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3481
msgid ""
"Summary bar now is colored yellow for warning situations such as: all tests "
"either were skipped or xpass/xfailed, or no tests were run at all (this is a "
"partial fix for issue500)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3485
msgid ""
"fix issue812: pytest now exits with status code 5 in situations where no "
"tests were run at all, such as the directory given in the command line does "
"not contain any tests or as result of a command line option filters all out "
"all tests (-k for example). Thanks Eric Siegerman (issue812) and Bruno "
"Oliveira for the PR."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../CHANGELOG.rst:3491
msgid ""
"Summary bar now is colored yellow for warning situations such as: all tests "
"either were skipped or xpass/xfailed, or no tests were run at all (related "
"to issue500). Thanks Eric Siegerman."
msgstr ""

