msgid ""
"New ``testpaths`` ini option: list of directories to search for tests when "
"executing pytest from the root directory. This can be used to speed up test "
"collection when a project has well specified directories for tests, being "
"usually more practical than configuring norecursedirs for all directories "
"that do not contain tests. Thanks to Adrian for idea (#694) and Bruno "
"Oliveira for the PR."
